I am a junior student at Turing Class, Peking University, advised by Dr. Yuqing Kong. I’m also working with Prof. Jason Hartline at Northwestern University.
Prof. Ariel Procaccia at Harvard. --My research interests lie in the areas of EconCS and algorithm design.
